            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
                    <h2>Welcome to the Secret Keeper App</h2>
                    <p>This application allows users to create, store, and manage their secrets securely.</p>
                    <h3>Features:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>User Authentication: Users can register, login, and logout securely.</li>
                        <li>Compose Secrets: Users can compose and publish their secrets.</li>
                        <li>View Secrets: Users can view their own secrets and read them in detail.</li>
                        <li>Delete Secrets: Users can delete their secrets when they are no longer needed.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h3>How to Use:</h3>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Register or login to your account.</li>
                        <li>Compose your secret by providing a title and content.</li>
                        <li>View your secrets on the home page. Click "Read more..." to view the full content.</li>
                        <li>Delete a secret by clicking the trash icon next to it.</li>
                        <li>Logout when done.</li>
                    </ol>
                    <p>Start sharing your secrets safely!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>    
    </body>
    
